Op_SET_PDS_DEMO ==
  /\ TRUE
  /\ pds' = "demo"
  /\ UNCHANGED << truth >>

Next ==
  \/ Op_SET_TRUTH_OTHER
  \/ Op_SET_TRUTH_PARTIAL
  \/ Op_SET_PDS_WORKING
  \/ Op_SET_PDS_DEMO

Spec == Init /\ [][Next]_vars

